        <div type="textpart" n="16" xml:id="part1">
          <head>Title of First Part</head>
          <ab n="27">
            <seg n="1">At postera luce duae praetoriae cohortes armatae templum Genetricis Veneris <app>
                <lem source="#Stuttg2 #L #al.">insedere</lem>
                <note>(Put.)</note>
              </app>; aditum senatus globus togatorum obsederat non occultis gladiis, dispersique
              per fora ac basilicas cunei militares. inter quorum aspectus et minas ingressi curiam
              senatores, et oratio principis per quaestorem eius audita est</seg>: <seg n="2">nemine
              nominatim compellato patres arguebat, quod publica munia desererent eorumque exemplo
              equites Romani ad <app><lem wit="#M">segnitiam</lem>
                <rdg wit="#al.">segnitiem</rdg>
              </app>
              <app>
                <lem wit="#L #Spir. #al.">uerterentur</lem>
                <rdg wit="#M">uterentur</rdg>
              </app>. etenim quid mirum e longinquis provinciis <app>
                <lem source="#Lips.">haud ueniri</lem>
                <rdg wit="#M">had ueniri</rdg>
                <witDetail wit="#M">fort.</witDetail>
                <rdgGrp>
                  <rdg>aduenire</rdg>
                  <note>uel</note>
                  <rdg wit="#al.">adueniri</rdg>
                </rdgGrp>
                <rdg wit="#Acid.">haud adueniri</rdg>
              </app>, cum plerique adepti consulatum et sacerdotia hortorum potius amoenitati
              inseruirent? quod velut telum corripuere accusatores</seg>.</ab>
          <!--Text goes here, according to the conventions laid out elsewhere in these guidelines.-->
        </div>
